data.description:
Welcome home to this charming ranch-style house nestled on a spacious 1/2 acre corner lot, offering breathtaking mountain views. This beautifully maintained property boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, providing ample space and comfort for your family's needs.
Enjoy the large Living Room and entertain in the spacious Family Room or curl up with a good book by the built in pellet stove. The bedrooms are separated from the living area, and provide plenty of privacy. Enjoy meal making time in the updated kitchen and attached dining area. 
Step outside onto your large covered patio and enjoy your backyard oasis. The half-acre corner lot offers room for gardening, play, or even the possibility of expanding your outdoor living space. And of course, those mountain views are the backdrop for all your outdoor activities.
Additional features of this exceptional property include ample storage throughout and a convenient location that provides easy access to nearby amenities and recreational opportunities.
Don't miss the chance to make this ranch-style gem your forever home. Experience the tranquility of high desert living, the comfort of spacious interiors, and the joy of an expansive backyard - all in one remarkable package. Come and tour this wonderful home today and start living your dreams.
